{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/blog/layout,_N_T_/blog/[slug]/layout,_N_T_/blog/[slug]/page,_N_T_/blog/squalene-olive-oil-skin-beauty-molecular/"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--R54jI80Dw697kr80tJYSc--><html lang=\"zh-TW\" class=\"__variable_930adb __variable_833e3a\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/3b891b14d3cf1415-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/604a121a6fa1a135-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/images/covers/squalene-olive-oil-skin-beauty-molecular.jpg\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/e0aad287a7bfe129.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/b13bb92b379b2030.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/51263da16d835ae4.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-f3c1a4c5383f0d5e.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-881ba9d46d833261.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-2b02549a5d25ddac.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/619-ba102abea3e3d0e4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/356-1cbf59d25a49fb83.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/blog/%5Bslug%5D/page-8a1ac09d2c5c1bba.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-54122d456140fd6d.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" sizes=\"any\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#4a5824\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://images.unsplash.com\"/><link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"https://images.unsplash.com\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/hero-grove.webp\" type=\"image/webp\" fetchPriority=\"high\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>橄欖油護膚的分子美學：為什麼角鯊烯（Squalene）是您肌膚最親密的仿生防護盾？｜知橄生活｜知橄生活 Olive Wisdom</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"您皮膚的皮脂中，天然就含有角鯊烯（Squalene），佔皮脂腺分泌物的13%。橄欖油是植物界含量最豐富的角鯊烯來源。這種驚人的生物相容性，正是為什麼地中海女性幾千年來的護膚秘密，正在被現代皮膚科學一一驗證。\"/><link rel=\"author\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"知橄生活研究團隊\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"橄欖油,特級初榨橄欖油,EVOO,地中海飲食,抗衰老,多酚,羥基酪醇,SIRT1,健康飲食\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta name=\"publisher\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/squalene-olive-oil-skin-beauty-molecular/\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"zh-TW\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/squalene-olive-oil-skin-beauty-molecular/\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"x-default\" href=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/squalene-olive-oil-skin-beauty-molecular/\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"橄欖油護膚的分子美學：為什麼角鯊烯（Squalene）是您肌膚最親密的仿生防護盾？\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"您皮膚的皮脂中，天然就含有角鯊烯（Squalene），佔皮脂腺分泌物的13%。橄欖油是植物界含量最豐富的角鯊烯來源。這種驚人的生物相容性，正是為什麼地中海女性幾千年來的護膚秘密，正在被現代皮膚科學一一驗證。\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/squalene-olive-oil-skin-beauty-molecular/\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"zh_TW\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/6121d0fbc8a3466fb8557d5fc8af1e45_0f0b7.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"橄欖油護膚的分子美學：為什麼角鯊烯（Squalene）是您肌膚最親密的仿生防護盾？\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2026-04-10\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:site\" content=\"@OliveWisdomTW\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"橄欖油護膚的分子美學：為什麼角鯊烯（Squalene）是您肌膚最親密的仿生防護盾？\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"您皮膚的皮脂中，天然就含有角鯊烯（Squalene），佔皮脂腺分泌物的13%。橄欖油是植物界含量最豐富的角鯊烯來源。這種驚人的生物相容性，正是為什麼地中海女性幾千年來的護膚秘密，正在被現代皮膚科學一一驗證。\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/6121d0fbc8a3466fb8557d5fc8af1e45_0f0b7.png\"/><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\",\"logo\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474979266404-7eaacbcd87c5?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80\",\"description\":\"為 35+ 知性追求者打造的橄欖油科學與美學空間\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"]}</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"bg-olive-50 text-gray-800 font-serif antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col __variable_930adb __variable_833e3a\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-olive-100 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\" class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><ellipse cx=\"14\" cy=\"14\" rx=\"5\" ry=\"8\" fill=\"#4a5824\" transform=\"rotate(-20 14 14)\"></ellipse><path d=\"M14 6 Q18 10 16 16 Q14 20 12 18\" stroke=\"#7a8f3a\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M14 8 Q9 6 8 12\" stroke=\"#4a5824\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.7\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col leading-none gap-0.5\"><spa